non_residential_details.development_type: Change of Use with Extension(s) over 999sqm

description: Single storey and fifth/sixth storey extensions, elevational alterations including recladding and change of use of first to fourth floors to 27 one bedroom and 95 two bedroom flats, and of ground and mezzanine floors and single storey extension for uses within Classes A1, A2, B1, D1 or D2 (Schedule 2, Part 3, Class E of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) Order 1995) with 129 car parking spaces at lower ground, ground and mezzanine floor levels at Albemarle House and 9 High Street, Beckenham
